                                      lines into this screen? What does
                                      the PR indent grid show? How does
                                      the system match PRs to the PO
                                      being created? How does the PR
                                      balance reduce after PO save? This
                                      is the primary workflow for this
                                      screen in daily use and it must be
                                      in Section 5. Please add this as
                                      Section 5.11 — PR to PO Conversion
                                      Workflow.<br>
